				<div class="row">
					<div class="2u 12u$(medium)">
						<p> </p>
						
						
					</div>
					<div class="8u 12u$(medium)" >
						<ul class="actions" >
							<li><font size="5pt">STEP1</font><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right fa-5x" ></i></li>
							<li><font size="4pt">STEP2</font><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right fa-3x" ></i></li>
							<li><font size="4pt">STEP3</font><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right fa-3x" ></i></li>
							<li><font size="4pt">STEP4</font><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right fa-3x" ></i></li>
						</ul>
						<h3>確認校友身份</h3>
						<!-- Box -->
						<div class="box">
							<p align="left">校友姓名：</p>
							<p align="left">部別：</p>
							<p align="left">學號：</p>
							<hr class="major" />
							<h4>請核對一下您的基本資料(若有異動，請回校友資料庫做修正)</h4>
							<div class="row " align="left">
								<div class="6u 12u$(small)">
									<p>郵遞地址:</p>
									<p>通訊電話:</p>
									<p>手機電話:</p>
									<p>永久地址:</p>
									<p>永久電話:</p>
									<p>永久傳真:</p>
								</div>
								<div class="6u$ 12u$(small)">
									<p>公司地址:</p>
									<p>公司名稱:</p>
									<p>職稱:</p>
									<p>公司電話:</p>
									<p>公司傳真:</p>
									<p>電子郵件:</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<hr class="major" />
							<h4>請選擇以下列何者地址作為收件地址？</h4>
							<form method="post" action="#">
								<div class="row uniform" >
									<!-- Break -->
									<div class="3u 12u$">
										<input type="radio" id="priority-low" name="priority" checked>
										<label for="priority-low">郵遞地址</label>
									</div>
									<div class="3u 12u$">
										<input type="radio" id="priority-normal" name="priority">
										<label for="priority-normal">公司地址</label>
									</div>
									<div class="3u 12u$">
										<input type="radio" id="priority-high" name="priority">
										<label for="priority-high">永久地址</label>
									</div>
									<div class="3u$ 12u$">
										<input type="radio" id="priority-high" name="priority">
										<label for="priority-high">代收地址</label>
									</div>
								</div>
							</form>
							<h4 >請輸入代收人及代收地址？</h4>
							<form method="post" action="#">
								<div class="row uniform" >
									<div class="4u 10u$(small)">
										<p>代收人姓名：</p>
									</div>
									<div class="6u$ 10u$(small)">
										<input type="text" name=" " id="" value="" placeholder="" />
									</div>
									<div class="4u 10u$(small)">
										<p>代收地址：</p>
									</div>
									<div class="6u$ 10u$(small)">
										<input type="text" name=" " id="" value="" placeholder="" />
									</div>
								</div>
							</form>
							<ul class="actions fit">
								<li><a href="線上申請代辦.html" class="button alt">回上一步</a></li>
								<li><a href="第二步.html" class="button">是，繼續下一步</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						
					</div>
					<div class="2u$ 12u$(medium)">
						<p> </p>
						
					</div>
					
				</div>
			</div>
